"The Odoo Calendar App is compatible with Outlook and Google Calendar. "
"Activate the sync in the Calendar App settings."
msgstr ""
"ແອັບປະຕິທິນ Odoo ສາມາດໃຊ້ຮ່ວມກັບ Outlook ແລະ Google Calendar ໄດ້. ທ່ານສາມາດເປີດການຊິງຄ໌ຂໍ້"
"ມູນໄດ້ໃນການຕັ້ງຄ່າແອັບປະຕິທິນ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"ທັງໝົດນີ້ແມ່ນໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຟຣີໃນການສະໝັກໃຊ້ປະຈຸບັນຂອງທ່ານ; ເຊີນທົດລອງໃຊ້ໄດ້ເລີຍ! 🙃"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This module provides a comprehensive suite of applications tailored to the "
"needs of therapy practices, empowering you to manage your business "
"efficiently and deliver exceptional patient care."
msgstr ""
"ໂມດູນນີ້ມອບຊຸດແອັບພລິເຄຊັນທີ່ຄົບຖ້ວນ ເຊິ່ງຖືກອອກແບບມາໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງການບໍລິການບຳບັດ, ຊ່"
"ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດຄຸ້ມຄອງທຸລະກິດໄດ້ຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບ ແລະ ມອບການເບິ່ງແຍງຄົນເຈັບທີ່ດີເລີດ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This opens up the <strong>Mail composer. </strong>Once you're in the "
"composer, just press the <strong>three dot icon </strong>in the toolbar, "
"then choose your desired <strong>email template</strong>."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ຈະເປີດ <strong>ຊ່ອງພິມອີເມລ. </strong>ເມື່ອທ່ານຢູ່ໃນຊ່ອງພິມແລ້ວ, ພຽງແຕ່ກົດ <strong>ໄອຄອນສາ"
"ມຈຸດ </strong>ໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມື, ແລ້ວເລືອກ <strong>ຕົວແບບອີເມລ</strong> ທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To begin, you'll find the key applications you need on your Odoo dashboard. "
"Let's take a closer look at how you can use these tools."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, ທ່ານຈະພົບແອັບພລິເຄຊັນຫຼັກທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃນ dashboard ຂອງ Odoo. ມາເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດວ່າມັ"
"ນໃຊ້ງານແນວໃດ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To create, edit and delete existing canned responses, just open the "
"<strong>Discuss App</strong>, then go to <strong>Configuration &gt; Canned "
"Responses</strong> and set up the message you'd like to easily send."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອສ້າງ, ແກ້ໄຂ ແລະ ລຶບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຕອບໄວ້ລ່ວງໜ້າ, ພຽງແຕ່ເປີດ <strong>ແອັບສົນທະນາ</strong>, ແລ້ວ"
"ໄປທີ່ <strong>ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ &gt; ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຕອບໄວ້ລ່ວງໜ້າ</strong> ແລະ ຕັ້ງຄ່າຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການສົ່ງໄ"
"ດ້ງ່າຍໆ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "To do so, go to CRM &gt; Configuration &gt; Sales Teams."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ໄປທີ່ CRM &gt; ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ &gt; ທີມຂາຍ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "To do that easily, you have two possibilities :"
msgstr "ເພື່ອເຮັດແນວນັ້ນໄດ້ງ່າຍໆ, ທ່ານມີສອງທາງເລືອກ:"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To reduce your no show rate drastically, appointments automatically comes "
"with reminders by Email and SMS."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອຫຼຸດຜ່ອນອັດຕາການບໍ່ມາຕາມນັດຢ່າງຫຼວງຫຼາຍ, ການນັດໝາຍຈະມີການແຈ້ງເຕືອນຜ່ານອີເມລ ແລະ SMS ໂດຍອັດຕ"
"ະໂນມັດ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Using Odoo, you can easily take notes during your appointments."
msgstr "ການໃຊ້ Odoo ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຈົດບັນທຶກໃນລະຫວ່າງການນັດໝາຍໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Welcome to the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Odoo Therapy Practice "
"package</font></strong>!"
msgstr ""
"ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບສູ່ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແພັກເກດ Odoo ສຳລັບການບໍລິການບຳບັດ"
"ສຸຂະພາບ</font></strong>!"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:wellness_practitioner.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບ! ຂໍໃຫ້ມ່ວນກັບການສຳຫຼວດ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model:appointment.type,name:wellness_practitioner.appointment_type_1
msgid "Wellness Session"
msgstr "ການບໍລິການສຸຂະພາບ"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປຶກສາກ່ຽວກັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານກັບພວກເຮົາ ຫຼື ຕ້ອງການໄປໃຫ້ໄກກວ່ານີ້ບໍ່?"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກແອັບທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ໃນໜ້າ dashboard ຫຼັກ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can also configure an email alias so everyone sending email to this one "
"will create a new opportunity for you."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າຊື່ແຝງອີເມລ (email alias) ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທຸກຄົນທີ່ສົ່ງອີເມລຫາທີ່ຢູ່ນີ້ ຈະສ້າງໂອກາດໃໝ່ໃຫ້ທ່ານໂ"
"ດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can even start a sound recording using the <strong>\"/voice transcript\""
" </strong>command !"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນການບັນທຶກສຽງໂດຍໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ <strong>\"/voice transcript\" </strong> ໄດ້"
"ເລີຍ!"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can set the consultation with an upfront online payment. Activate it in "
"your Appointment Type Settingsby setting up an upfront payment method."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າການປຶກສາດ້ວຍການຊຳລະເງິນອອນລາຍລ່ວງໜ້າ. ເປີດໃຊ້ງານໃນການຕັ້ງຄ່າປະເພດການນັດໝາຍໂດ"
"ຍການກຳນົດວິທີການຊຳລະເງິນລ່ວງໜ້າ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ສຳເລັດຕົວຢ່າງການນຳໃຊ້ນີ້ແລ້ວ! ຍັງມີອີກຫຼາຍລ້ານວິທີໃນການປັບແຕ່ງ Odoo ໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການ"
"ຂອງທຸລະກິດທ່ານ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries"
" &gt; Upgrade your Therapy Practice package and check the related box."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ, ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້. ໄປທີ່ ແອັບ &gt; ໝວດອຸດສາຫະກຳ &gt; ອັບເກຣດ"
"ແພັກເກດ Therapy Practice ແລະ ໝາຍຕິກໃນຫ້ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You may also create a personalized website in a few clicks by adding the "
"Website App, your appointment page will be automatically added."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດສ້າງເວັບໄຊສ່ວນຕົວໄດ້ໃນບໍ່ກີ່ຄລິກໂດຍການເພີ່ມແອັບເວັບໄຊ, ໜ້າການນັດໝາຍຂອງທ່ານຈະຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າ"
"ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You receive a call from a new potential patient, Emily, who is interested in"
" your therapy services."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບສາຍຈາກຄົນເຈັບໃໝ່ທີ່ມີທ່າແຮງ, Emily, ຜູ້ທີ່ສົນໃຈໃນການບໍລິການບຳບັດຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຄວນຈະສາມາດລອງເຮັດຕາມຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ ເພື່ອເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງຂະບວນການຕ່າງໆທີ່ທ່ານສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ຢ່າງວ່"
"ອງໄວດ້ວຍແພັກເກດນີ້ໃນ Odoo."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "academy"
msgstr "ສະຖາບັນ"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "and"
msgstr "ແລະ"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານປະກອບ"

